  newsTitle: '创业者被投资人玩儿死的100种花样',
  newsDate: 1507542948000,
  photoPath: 'http://guoanchuangke2.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image/test/94091502351935.jpg',
  unpayednewsInstruction: `<p>
	<img width="100%" src="http://guoanchuangke2.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/dapingtai/image/20170810/1.gif" alt=""> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">几天前，毕马威发布的风险投资基金（风投）投资趋势全球季度报告《风投脉搏》显示，受大型交易数量增加的推动，风投在</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">2017</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">年第二季度对中国初创企业的投资增长了两倍至</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">107</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">亿美元！</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;"></span><img src="http://guoanchuangke2.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/dapingtai/image/20170810/2.png" alt=""> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">没错！金主爸爸们就是这么爱买买买，投资热潮不断，数据涨势明显，如此巨额的资金不知道又把多少小猪猪吹上了风口。然鹅，有钱紧接着的下一个关键词可能是</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">……</span><strong><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">任性</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">……</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<strong><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">创投圈儿大了，什么样的金主爸爸都有</span><strong><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">。</span></strong><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;"></span></strong><span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">十多年前，活跃在中国的投资方大多是国外机构的中国办事处，这些</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">海派</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">或</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">海归</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">的投资人都会遵守很多行业的基本准则。但随着更多海外资本的不断涌入以及大量</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">土鳖</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”VC</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">的崛起，加上在中国市场环境的耳濡目染后，这个群体中有些个体（注意：是个体，不是整体）已经开始出现变质和病态。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">越来越多的</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">VC</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">和天使投资人，被大批亟待解决融资问题的创业者们</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">惯坏了</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">。不守时的、架子大的、动不动就说创业不靠谱的、不做自我介绍的、不懂装懂的、不带名片的、谈了一年还说要继续观察的、满嘴跑产业理想的、爱说自己跟马云马化腾很熟的</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">……</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span style="line-height:1.5;color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;"></span><img src="http://guoanchuangke2.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/dapingtai/image/20170810/3.png" alt=""> 
</p>
<p style="text-indent:21.0pt;">
	<span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">小孩子才分对错，成年人只看利弊</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">在残酷的商战中被突显得淋漓尽致</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">。</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">执着于</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">对与错</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">的人被认为是幼稚天真的，对于创业者来说，不惜一切代价</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">活下来</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">才是唯一重要的事情。然而有些</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">VC</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">真的可能让你</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">“</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">活不下来</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">”</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">，沟通中的小细节暂且不论，下面这些投资人挖的坑，才可能直接影响到创业者的生死。无论你是亲身经历还是道听途说，一定觉得似曾相识</span><span style="color:#000000;font-family:'Microsoft YaHei';font-size:14px;">……</span> 
</p>`,
